{"tid":686590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣 22K 慘被 大陸人 恥笑?! 阿共仔「薪情」是這樣…","createTime":"2018-06-01T11:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T17:42:03.000Z","uid":53060,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a13ba3f0c64148755bdc58c079bb3c8c5f4dafcc","tid":686590,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣低薪問題近日再度被網友提出討論，連中國官媒《人民日報》也忍不住嘲笑，稱<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「22K」已成台灣代表性數字</span></span>，不過細看<span style=\"color: red;\">中國各城市的薪資水平，起薪低於19K的勞工仍佔最多數</span>，「薪情」大概不會比台灣好。<br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，人力資源網「智聯招聘」的薪資水平指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">月薪介於4000元人民幣（約新台幣1萬8972元）到6000元人民幣的職缺仍是最多</span>，佔了32.6％，介於6000到8000元人民幣的職缺佔21.1％，等於是有超過5成起薪介於4000至8000元人民幣。另外有3成職缺起薪至少8000元人民幣（約新台幣3萬7944元）。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，中國1線城市的平均薪水約8000元到1萬元人民幣，但2線城市的薪水就要打個6折，且1線城市房價和消費超高，繳完5種社會保險和住房公積金（5險1金）、房租等細項，錢也剩下不多，<span style=\"color: red;\">生活不比台灣輕鬆</span>。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計，中國37個主要城市平均月薪為7789元人民幣（約新台幣3萬6943元），北京以1萬310元人民幣（約新台幣4萬8900元）排名第1。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180509/1349984/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180509%2F1349984%2F&d=csMR%2BlC7F6CY5uLdTPNITy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6b7212a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180509%2F1349984%2F&h=155487c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180509/1349984/</a>"},{"pid":"d4530d3f9eacc42efe52d6b515e4c6badb8c544a","tid":686590,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180509/640_25053d2403ac1a4b0160cb44e98d2567.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180509%2F640_25053d2403ac1a4b0160cb44e98d2567.jpg&h=1d454940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據統計，中國主要城市平均月薪超過3.6萬元台幣，以北京等1線城市居前。但光看平均數值，難以瞭解其中高低落差。路透<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180509/640_756680de882d7d35303720f13950d4e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180509%2F640_756680de882d7d35303720f13950d4e3.jpg&h=3dddee06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年第4季中國38個主要城市平均月薪（單位：人民幣）。翻攝「第一財經」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180509/640_fe2f01b1c4e1e2e9ae8e0d8bf713251c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180509%2F640_fe2f01b1c4e1e2e9ae8e0d8bf713251c.jpg&h=44b27fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年第1季中國38個主要城市平均月薪（單位：人民幣）。翻攝「中國新聞網」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180509/640_4c40db2c865e21908695521f7f68c9ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180509%2F640_4c40db2c865e21908695521f7f68c9ce.jpg&h=55d39057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n智聯招聘發布中國主要城市平均薪資逼近8000元人民幣後，對岸網友紛紛表示「扎心」，或自己是「拖後腿」的。翻攝搜狐"},{"pid":"5de758a5c73b6a6ece05f7f941bef0b329ddca94","tid":686590,"uid":38904,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:01:48.000Z","msg":"人哋22k就可以買啲真嘅嘢食<br />\n支那嗰啲買啲唔食得嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56ffaee2c8cd46c010b9dd3e8136208f4271102","tid":686590,"uid":135767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"30d6fd57cdf8a53637f6d938fbaf4c2acd943be1","tid":686590,"uid":99173,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:42:11.000Z","msg":"上年台灣畢業直接台灣做野<br />\n平均一個月50K <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile